  "remarks": "The 185th Center for Combat Use and Combat Purpose of the Aerospace Forces “Ashuluk” is a weapons training ground of the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation. It is used in particular to test anti-aircraft and other types of missiles, which are used by the Russian military in Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
